==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hamshackle
<hw>Ham"shac`kle</hw> <pr>(h⟦acr⟧m"sh⟦acr⟧k`'l)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Ham</ets> + <ets>shackle</ets>.]</ety> <def>To fasten (an
animal) by a rope binding the head to one of the fore legs; <as>as, to
<ex>hamshackle</ex> a horse or cow</as>; hence, to bind or restrain; to
curb.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hamster</ent>⟦br⟧
